## Installation âš™ï¸

1. **Download the Extension:**  
   - Clone this repository or download the extension from the https://github.com/leconkisador/lichessMods.git page. ğŸŒ

2. **Install the Extension:**  
   - Follow the installation instructions for your browser:  
     - *Google Chrome:* Go to Chrome Menu â†’ More Tools â†’ Extensions. Enable "Developer mode" and click "Load unpacked." Select the extension folder. ğŸ“‚  
     - *Mozilla Firefox:* Open Add-ons Manager (about:addons), click the gear icon, and choose "Install Add-on From File." Select the extension folder. ğŸ¦Š

3. **Activate the Mod:**  
   - Visit lichess.org and click on the LichessMods icon in your browser toolbar. ğŸ”§  
   - Choose a predefined mod or create your own using the customization options. ğŸ‰

